request.description:
This api will generate the token from MMC.
Select "Basic Auth" as a AUTHORISATION type.
Content-type:application/x-www-form-urlencoded
grant_type:client_credentials as BODY

This will return the application id.
QueryParam : external reference id, which is generated from code generator in the code.
Bearer token generated in the sign in api needs to be passed in the authorisation.
